---
title: Tuscan-Spiced Shrimp with Pesto Couscous, Blistered Grape Tomatoes & Zucchini
description: Looking for a hearty meal that will fill you up (without weighing you down)? Seafood is your best bet! This dish features shrimp seasoned in our spicy blend of Tuscan herbs, piled next to a savory pesto and almond couscous. Zucchini and grape tomatoes are served on the side, after a quick sauté turns tomatoes juicy and slightly blistered. Shrimp is finished with more pesto on top for a light seafood dinner with a rich Tuscan twist!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/tuscan-spiced-shrimp-98fe7986.jpg
